OL,3,CCollege workers turned into AI
OL,4,Cgirlfriends by student tell of
OL,5,Cstalking ordeal
OL,7,FAmber and Courtney told ITV News West
OL,8,FCountry they were horrified by
OL,9,Fmaterial their stalker collected
OL,11,FTwo college staff members who were
OL,12,Fstalked by a student say the
OL,13,Fexperience has left them feeling
OL,14,F"tainted" and "dirty".
OL,16,FAmber Wilson and Courtney Blackmore
OL,17,Fexperienced a number of inappropriate
OL,18,Fencounters with a pupil while working
OL,19,Fat Petroc College before noticing him
OL,20,Ftaking photos of them.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@IO]vD@OOUvD@UO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
