OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1776708665
OL,3,CCollege workers turned into AI
OL,4,Cgirlfriends by student tell of
OL,5,Cstalking ordeal
OL,7,FFollowing an investigation it was
OL,8,Fdiscovered that Ethan Fenwick had
OL,9,Fcollated thousands of photos and voice
OL,10,Fnotes of the pair and had also
OL,11,Fproduced AI chat versions of his
OL,12,Fvictims for him to talk to.
OL,14,FCourtney told ITV West Country: "It
OL,15,Fdrives you crazy. It really does.
OL,17,F"I didn't think that humans were
OL,18,Fcapable of this kind of thing, let
OL,19,Falone did I ever think that I would be
OL,20,Fa victim of it.
OL,26,@vD@aOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
