OL,3,CCollege workers turned into AI
OL,4,Cgirlfriends by student tell of
OL,5,Cstalking ordeal
OL,7,F"And the mental impact it's had on me
OL,8,Fthat's not just something that you
OL,9,Frecover from within a day."
OL,11,FAmber first became wary when Fenwick,
OL,12,Fthen aged 17, asked her to prom. The
OL,13,Ffollowing year, then 18, he asked her
OL,14,Fon a date to which she again refused.
OL,16,FA few weeks later, Amber spotted
OL,17,FFenwick secretly taking a photograph
OL,18,Fof her, before he sent her a friend
OL,19,Frequest on social media a few days
OL,20,Flater.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@[O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
