OL,3,CCollege workers turned into AI
OL,4,Cgirlfriends by student tell of
OL,5,Cstalking ordeal
OL,7,FBoth Amber and Courtney then received
OL,8,Ftwo further Instagram account friend
OL,9,Frequests, with the account biography
OL,10,Fstating the owner wanted to kidnap the
OL,11,Fwomen and 'use their bodies'.
OL,13,FThe women reported their concerns to
OL,14,Fthe police who discovered a huge
OL,15,Fnumber of pictures and videos of the
OL,16,Fpair - many digitally altered,
OL,17,Fcollaged, and combined with pictures
OL,18,Ftaken from social media.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
