OL,3,CCollege workers turned into AI
OL,4,Cgirlfriends by student tell of
OL,5,Cstalking ordeal
OL,7,FThey also discovered Fenwick had
OL,8,Fsecretly been recording their voices
OL,9,Fand been using online programs to find
OL,10,Fand locate all social media accounts
OL,11,Flinked to both victims and others.
OL,13,FHe had created AI versions of his
OL,14,Fvictims, using covertly captured audio
OL,15,Fand pictures, with a chat facility
OL,16,Fenabling him to talk to their fake
OL,17,Fpersona.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
