OL,3,CCollege workers turned into AI
OL,4,Cgirlfriends by student tell of
OL,5,Cstalking ordeal
OL,7,FReflecting on when she first witnessed
OL,8,Fthe evidence for herself, Amber said:
OL,9,F"These were photos of me from when I
OL,10,Fwas younger. Things that I wouldn't
OL,11,Feven know how to find.
OL,13,F"Then there were thousands of photos
OL,14,Fof me at work, videos of me at work,
OL,15,Fjust doing my job, helping him,
OL,16,Fhelping other students.
OL,26,@qD@AOUuD@AOU
