OL,3,CCollege workers turned into AI
OL,4,Cgirlfriends by student tell of
OL,5,Cstalking ordeal
OL,7,F"Voice memos of things that I was
OL,8,Fsaying again at work, I could hear
OL,9,Fmyself saying other students names, I
OL,10,Fcould almost reimagine myself in these
OL,11,Fsituations."
OL,13,FOf the AI content she added: "I don't
OL,14,Fthink I really realised how easy it
OL,15,Fwas for someone to use these tools in
OL,16,Fsuch an evil way.
OL,18,F"That's our voice. That's our body.
OL,19,FThat's our face. And he has literally
OL,20,Fcrafted it into what he wants us to
OL,21,Fbe."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@LO]uD@^OUzD@AOU}D@DO]
