OL,3,CCollege workers turned into AI
OL,4,Cgirlfriends by student tell of
OL,5,Cstalking ordeal
OL,7,FCourtney added: "There were photos
OL,8,Fwhere it looks like I'm staring right
OL,9,Fat the camera, and, and I sit there
OL,10,Fand I think. How did I, how did I not
OL,11,Fknow?
OL,13,F"I'm just stood doing a job that I
OL,14,Flove. I'm working with students that
OL,15,Freally, really need my help.
OL,17,F"I'm doing the best job I can possibly
OL,18,Fdo and yet somehow, I've still got
OL,19,Fsomebody that has taken advantage of
OL,20,Fme."
OL,26,@oD@QOUuD@AOUyD@AOU|D@DO]
