OL,3,CCollege workers turned into AI
OL,4,Cgirlfriends by student tell of
OL,5,Cstalking ordeal
OL,7,FFenwick, 19, pleaded guilty to two
OL,8,Fcounts of stalking involving serious
OL,9,Falarm or distress at Exeter Crown
OL,10,FCourt in January this year.
OL,12,FHe was handed a three year community
OL,13,Forder, consisting of a rehabilitation
OL,14,Factivity requirement and 150 hours of
OL,15,Funpaid work.
OL,17,FLifetime restraining orders were put
OL,18,Fin place to protect Amber and
OL,19,FCourtney, and a sexual harm prevention
OL,20,Forder was also granted.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
