OL,3,CCollege workers turned into AI
OL,4,Cgirlfriends by student tell of
OL,5,Cstalking ordeal
OL,7,FBut his victims say despite the case
OL,8,Fconcluding in court they are still
OL,9,Fliving with the impact the stalking
OL,10,Fhad on them.
OL,12,FAmber said: "I am now changed forever.
OL,13,FMy mind does not work the same. I
OL,14,Fcan't trust things the way I used to
OL,15,Fbe. I can't trust people the way I
OL,16,Fused to.
OL,26,@tD@MOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
