PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1776708665
OL,3,CCollege workers turned into AI
OL,4,Cgirlfriends by student tell of
OL,5,Cstalking ordeal
OL,7,F"I could move to the other side of the
OL,8,Fworld, I think and I'd always have
OL,9,Fthose thoughts. I will carry with me
OL,10,Ffor the rest of my life. I can't just
OL,11,Fbrush it off.
OL,13,F"It's almost like I feel dirty and it
OL,14,Fdoesn't matter how much I shower, I
OL,15,Fcan't get rid of the dirt. That's how
OL,16,Fit feels."
OL,26,@xD@JO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
