OL,3,CCollege workers turned into AI
OL,4,Cgirlfriends by student tell of
OL,5,Cstalking ordeal
OL,7,FCourtney added: "Although we have some
OL,8,Famazing, amazing, restraints and
OL,9,Fthings in place, it never really
OL,10,Fleaves you. I don't think I'll ever
OL,11,Ffeel truly safe again.
OL,13,F"It changes your perspective
OL,14,Fcompletely. I second guess everybody,
OL,15,Fanybody that walks past me.
OL,17,F"I'm still in the job. I love my job.
OL,18,FI try not to let it affect my
OL,19,Frelationships with other students, but
OL,20,FI'm a lot more on edge."
OL,26,@oD@QOUuD@AOUyD@AOU|D@XO]
